


# Roadmap

## Strategic Roadmap 2025—2027

### Q3 2025 — Core Protocol for HyroTrader Case Study

* Launch of core protocol features on Solana mainnet

* Integration with initial trading venues (Bybit, CLEO, OKX)

* Basic challenge system deployment

* Alpha version of manager verification system

### Q4 2025 — Q2 2026 — Extended Protocol for Prop Firm Onboarding

* Full trader reputation system rollout

* Advanced risk management features

* Multi-venue trading optimization

* Enhanced performance analytics dashboard

### Q2 2026 — Q4 2026 — Extended for many use cases

* Cross-chain bridge implementations

* Automated trading strategy marketplace

* Advanced oracle network deployment

* Extended DeFi protocol integrations

### Mid 2027 — Fully decentralized protocol for accessible for everyone 

* Decentralized governance transition

* Institutional-grade API service

* Advanced derivatives support

* Global regulatory compliance framework
